{"tid":153459,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【兩會】人大代表倡食安罪納危害公共安全罪　嚴重可判死刑","createTime":"2017-03-12T15:01:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-13T07:38:34.000Z","uid":22675,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"18bb77a3a3a63fe398f6c0298e1235cb65395f96","tid":153459,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:01:16.000Z","msg":"北京正在召開兩會，全國人大代表及民革貴州省委副主委鲍家科建議將食品安全罪名納入危害公共安全罪，更建議如果情況嚴重，可以判處死刑。<br />\n<img src=\"http://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170312/s00004/1489295646779_4AD27A12F50F6652BFFB5911FD30A79D.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170312%2Fs00004%2F1489295646779_4AD27A12F50F6652BFFB5911FD30A79D.jpg&h=4d9f1ec0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n報道指，鲍家科認為食安犯罪仍然相當多，除了因為犯案人的食安觀念薄弱，被高回報吸引而鋌而走險外，刑法的不足亦是一個重要原因。<br />\n他指現時食安相關的罪名屬於《刑法》第三章中「破壞社會主義市場經濟秩序罪」，這類罪行法律所保護的主要利益是國家對食安的監督管理秩序，但他認為，食安問題中法律所保護的利益應該是多方面的，當中包括「多數人的生命權、健康權及重大公私財產的安全」。<br />\n鲍家科指，食品是日常生活最基礎的東西，食安罪行對市場秩序的破壞較為次要，但會徹底及直接地危害​公共安全。<br />\n（澎湃新聞）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170312/s00004/1489295655375\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170312%2Fs00004%2F1489295655375&d=xz9%2BKahtnlDLfwjNDOwuFDACEZ5EYDiH2DLr%2FNuFFp4%3D&h=ac7ba640\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170312%2Fs00004%2F1489295655375&h=6ca9529d\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170312/s00004/1489295655375</a>"},{"pid":"29d516b558937188f12c4994c5bdfc7cc52b5ed5","tid":153459,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:17:48.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"6e142cc8e17b431b49be88d60daee20dacd4c31a","tid":153459,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T15:19:38.000Z","msg":"權鬥<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 